Name: ASHOK JEWELLERS INC
Page Description:
At Ashok Jewellers, tradition meets excellence.

From our roots in Punjab, India, to opening our first Toronto store in 1985, our family’s passion for jewellery has spanned five generations.

Today, our flagship in Mississauga’s Ashok Jewellers Plaza showcases a world of craftsmanship — sourcing fine designs from Singapore, Dubai, Malaysia, Turkey, Italy, and beyond.

A legacy of heritage, artistry, and trust — proudly shared with our community.

Name: BIJOUTERIE ORLY - CARREFOUR LAVAL
Address Line 1: Carrefour Laval - 3035 boulevard le carrefour local
Page Description:
Welcome to ORLY Jewellers, a family owned jewelry and Swiss watches retail store founded in 1999. We are a high-end boutique that is committed to providing our customers with the most exquisite and luxurious jewelry and watches from renowned brands around the world.

As a family owned business, we pride ourselves on offering a personalized and attentive service to each and every customer. Our team of knowledgeable and experienced staff are dedicated to helping you find the perfect piece of jewelry or watch that suits your unique style and taste.

At ORLY Jewellers, we understand the significance of jewelry and watches in people's lives, and that's why we only offer the finest quality pieces that are both timeless and contemporary. Our collection is carefully curated to reflect the latest trends in the industry, while also featuring classic designs that will stand the test of time.

In addition to our wide selection of jewelry and watches, we also offer expert repair services and appraisals to ensure that your cherished pieces remain in top condition. We take great pride in our craftsmanship and attention to detail, and strive to provide a level of service that exceeds our customers' expectations.

We invite you to visit our store and experience the luxury and elegance that ORLY Jewellers has to offer. Whether you are looking for a special occasion piece or a cherished gift for a loved one, we are confident that our collection will inspire and delight you. Thank you for choosing ORLY Jewellers, we look forward to serving you.

Customers trust Finch Centre Jewellers to provide the latest in men's and women's fashion, whether they're searching for diamond engagement rings, elegant necklaces, or premium watches.

Name: RADIANT FINE JEWELLERS UPPER CANADA MALL
Page Title: RADIANT FINE JEWELLERS UPPER CANADA MALL
Page Description:
FOR OVER 20 YEARS, OUR FOUNDERS HAVE DESIGNED AND IMPORTED ELEGANT, STYLISH JEWELLERY WITH AN EMPHASIS ON QUALITY AND NOVELTY.
AS OUR SECOND GENERATION OF THE FAMILY CONTINUES THE JOURNEY, WE STRIVE IN MAINTAINING OLD WORLD TRADITIONS WHILE IMPLEMENTING CUTTING-EDGE TECHNOLOGY. OUR COMMITMENT TO THE INDUSTRY IS ENGRAINED IN OUR DNA WITH FOCUS ON PRODUCT SELECTION AND EXCEPTIONAL SERVICE.
WITH A WIDE VARIETY OF PRECIOUS STONES, DIAMONDS, AND METALS, ALONG WITH TRADITIONAL TOOLS AND CONTEMPORARY AIDS, SUCH AS COMPUTER-AIDED-DESIGN (CAD) TECHNOLOGY, OUR CRAFTSMEN HAVE THE MEANS TO DESIGN PIECES THAT CREATE MEMORIES FOR A LIFETIME.
OUR RANGE OF EXPERTISE DOES NOT STOP IN THE REALM OF PRECIOUS STONES AND METALS. TIMEPIECES ARE ANOTHER SIGNIFICANT PART OF OUR BUSINESS. WE CONTINUALLY TRAIN AND UPDATE OUR KNOWLEDGE ON NEW FEATURES INTRODUCED IN EVERY BRAND OF WATCHES WE CARRY.
WE UNDERSTAND THE NEED TO BRING FUN, TRENDY, AND FASHIONABLE BRANDS TO THE FOREFRONT. THIS IS WHY OUR PRODUCT LINE INCLUDES SUCH BRANDS AS ANIA HAIE, THOMAS SABO, AND UNOARRE, TO NAME A FEW.
WE UNDERSTAND THAT PURCHASING JEWELLERY CAN BE AN EXTENSIVE EXPERIENCE. OUR TRADITION OF BRINGING QUALITY PRODUCTS TO OUR CUSTOMERS AND PROVIDING THE BEST CUSTOMER SERVICE – FOR LONG AFTER A PIECE LEAVES THE STORE – AIMS TO EASE THOSE FEARS. AT RADIANT FINE JEWELLERS CUSTOMER SATISFACTION AND QUALITY CRAFTMANSHIP ARE THE CORNERSTONES OF OUR BUSINESS.

Name: RICHARDSONS JEWELLERY
Page Description:
Richardsons Jewellery is a community-oriented fine jewellery store owned and operated by the Fisher family in Lloydminster, Alberta/ Saskatchewan. Our goal is to serve you with quality fine jewellery, build relationships in surrounding communities, and help you celebrate life’s biggest moments with fine jewellery and timepieces.  

Historically, Richardson’s Jewellery has a long heritage dating back to 1967, when the Richardson’s family opened the first doors in Regina, Saskatchewan. The store grew and expanded into many locations. And in 1979, the door of Lloydminster opened. After several years of managing the store, Juergen Schwenk had the opportunity to purchase the store in 1989. With many years of great success, Juergen knew retirement would be in the future and in 2002 he started looking for the next family to run the business.
